annotations.description: Going into the blustery season why not drink something both refreshing and Seasonal? If you've been watching this channel for any length of time you'll know ...
annotations.title: Apple's Eye Buck

textContent:
1oz (30ml) Aged Rum
1oz (30ml) Applejack (or Calvados VSOP)
.75oz (22.5ml) Ginger Syrup
.5oz (15ml) Lime Juice
3 Dashes Angostura Bitters (Optional)
Top Club Soda

Shake and pour over ice. Top with soda
